OLT/PON Manager — Session OLT-1
Owns:
  • Idempotent SQLite tables: olts, pon_ports, onus, olt_alerts,
    olt_alert_rules, olt_polls, olt_settings
  • Admin web pages at /admin/olt/{dashboard,onus,alerts,system-config}
